This package contains Haskell bindings authored for the haskell-conjunction
project and distributed under the BSD-3-Clause license in LICENSE.

The vendored SGP4 implementation under sgp4/ is David A. Vallado's reference
SGP4 companion code for Fundamentals of Astrodynamics and Applications. The
source headers identify the code as companion code by David Vallado and cite
the 2006 AIAA paper by Vallado, Crawford, Hujsak, and Kelso, "Revisiting
Spacetrack Report #3."

The SGP4 code is included as third-party source for interoperability. Public
domain provenance is based on Vallado's stated intent in correspondence
preserved by the U.S. Naval Research Laboratory Tracker Component Library.
The BSD-3-Clause license for this Haskell package should not be read as
relicensing the vendored SGP4 source.
